text: Aliaksei Shynkel (born 6 July 1994) is a Belarusian handball player for SKA Minsk and the Belarusian national team.EHF profile He participated at the 2017 World Men's Handball Championship.2017 World Championship roster ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Grodno Category:Belarusian male handball players
